---
title: Sarh — Officer + Department Manager user flow (with NFT minting)
---
flowchart TD
    A([Officer / manager signs in]) --> B[/Dashboard/]
    B --> C{Role?}
    C -- registry_officer / reviewer --> Q[Queue]
    C -- department_manager --> M[Approvals queue]
    C -- id_issuer --> I[Issue station]
    C -- super_admin / auditor --> AD[Admin console]

    Q --> Q1[Filter: pending / under_review / needs_clarification]
    Q1 --> Q2[Open property]
    Q2 --> Q3[Review hero details + map<br/>+ run spatial conflict check]
    Q3 --> Q4{Decision}
    Q4 -- Recommend approval --> Q5[Optional technical note]
    Q5 --> Q6[POST /properties/:id/review<br/>decision=recommend_approval]
    Q6 --> Q7[status=under_review<br/>routed to manager]

    Q4 -- Needs clarification --> Q9[Required note]
    Q9 --> Q10[POST review<br/>decision=needs_clarification]
    Q10 --> Q11[Owner notified]

    Q4 -- Reject --> Q12[Required reason]
    Q12 --> Q13[POST review<br/>decision=reject]
    Q13 --> Q14[Owner notified + reason]

    M --> M1[Filter: under_review]
    M1 --> M2[Open property + officer report]
    M2 --> M3{Final decision}
    M3 -- Reject --> M4[Required reason]
    M4 --> M5[POST /final-approve<br/>decision=reject]
    M3 -- Approve --> M6[Enter decree number]
    M6 --> M7[POST /final-approve<br/>decision=approve + decree]
    M7 --> M8[Server: PAdES-sign deed<br/>+ issue SSI VC<br/>+ pin metadata to IPFS<br/>+ mint NFT on blockchain<br/>+ stamp QR]
    M8 --> M9[Notify owner — deed + NFT ready]

    I --> I1[5-step wizard:<br/>identity → photo → signature →<br/>fingerprint → review]
    I1 --> I2[Create citizen record]
    I2 --> I3[Issue card +<br/>encode NFC + sign VC]

    AD --> AD1[Properties map]
    AD --> AD2[Citizens / Officers users]
    AD --> AD3[Digital IDs roster]
    AD --> AD4[NFT licences ledger]
    AD --> AD5[Audit log]
    AD --> AD6[Reports KPIs]
